title: "I bumped into Tobey 20 minutes later!" Tom Holland and Zendaya on the Spider-Man WhatsApp group 🕷
author: BBC Radio 1
description:
Watch Tom and Zendaya's chat with Ali in full on BBC iPlayer in the UK: https://bbc.in/3rOThNW

Tom Holland and Zendaya join BBC Radio 1's film critic Ali Plumb to talk about new Marvel movie, Spider-Man: No Way Home. Tom reveals all about his Spider-Man WhatsApp group with Andrew Garfield and Tobey Maguire. Ali brings up Tom's blooper reaction face. And Zendaya does a perfect Peter Parker impression.

#TomHolland #Zendaya #SpiderManNoWayHome 

Watch more of Movies with Ali Plumb on BBC iPlayer in the UK: https://www.bbc.co.uk/tv/radio1
Including Movies That Made Me with some of the world's biggest movie stars.
